                        "metadata": Object {},
                        "page-url": "/story/ecfc249c-a760-49b5-bfd6-485773ab14c6/element/70c4126f-b3df-4809-8bac-15146e5c6496",
                        "subtype": null,
                        "text": "<p>The political crisis, triggered by the resignation of 22 members of the Congress party in Madhya Pradesh, was brought to an end after the Supreme Court directed for a floor test on March 19.</p>",
                        "title": "",
                        "type": "text",
                      },
                      Object {
                        "description": "",
